  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Once you have set up the Square integration, added a payment device, and are ready to accept payments, you will need to assign the Square device to your VCT.</p><h3 id=\"IntegratedPaymentsSetup:AssigningaSquareTerminaltoaVirtualCashTerminal(VCT)toAcceptPayments-PreviousSteps\">Previous Steps</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936588814/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Add+a+Square+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936588814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Adding a Square Payment Device in RepairQ</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936556034/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Activating+Square+Integration+in+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936556034\" data-linked-resource-version=\"15\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Activating Square Integration in RepairQ</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"IntegratedPaymentsSetup:AssigningaSquareTerminaltoaVirtualCashTerminal(VCT)toAcceptPayments-NextStep\">Next Step</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936719893/Integrated+Payments+Accepting+Payments+on+a+Square+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936719893\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments: Accepting Payments on a Square Terminal</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"IntegratedPaymentsSetup:AssigningaSquareTerminaltoaVirtualCashTerminal(VCT)toAcceptPayments-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934295157/Integrated+Payment+Processing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934295157\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payment Processing - Start Here!</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785459/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentsSetup:AssigningaSquareTerminaltoaVirtualCashTerminal(VCT)toAcceptPayments-ParingyourSquareTerminalWithYourVCT\">Paring your Square Terminal With Your VCT</h2><p /><p>1. On the top navigation bar, click the <strong>Location Shortname Dropdown</strong> on the upper right of the page. In the drop-down section, click Assign VCT.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785459/Integration%20Setup%2015.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: You can also do this by clicking <strong>Assign a VCT</strong>&quot; link under the Get Started section of the RepairQ dashboard.</p><p /><p>2. On the Terminal Management screen, click the <strong>Assign button (Play icon)</strong> under the Actions column to assign VCT.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785459/Integration%20Setup%2016.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. Select which payment types you want to accept on your VCT. Make sure to select <strong>Accept Credit Card</strong> to process card payments on your terminal. On the Payment Device dropdown, <strong>select the Square device that will be paired with this VCT</strong>.  Once you are satisfied with your selection(s) click <strong>Start</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785459/Integration%20Setup%2017.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: If you select <strong>Accept Cash</strong>, you will also need to enter the starting cash amount in your cash drawer.</p><p /><p>4. The Terminal Management screen will now show that your VCT is assigned.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785459/Integration%20Setup%2019.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
